## ğŸš€ Features

- âœ… Upload skin lesion images
- ğŸ” Predict dermatological conditions using an EfficientNet-B0 model
- ğŸ§  Explain predictions using Grad-CAM heatmaps
- ğŸ“„ Display clinical recommendations per disease
- ğŸ’» Lightweight Flask application, easy to deploy

---

## ğŸ› ï¸ Tech Stack

- **Language**: Python 3.8+
- **Web Framework**: Flask
- **Deep Learning**: PyTorch, TorchVision
- **Model**: EfficientNet-B0 (transfer learning)
- **Visualization**: Grad-CAM, Matplotlib
- **Frontend**: HTML/CSS with Jinja2 templates

